## Robots and How They Change Society

Whether or not we like it, robots are impacting our lives.  We need to consider how our society is changing because of new technology.  Often times the tasks we want robots to carry out are for our benefit - entertainment, to be helpful, to assist in dangerous circumstances, do tedious work or even perform work that is problematic for humans to do themselves.

